		<div class="pts"></div>
        <h6>The Social Platform  for Customer Relationship Building</h6>
        <p> When your company  joins IdeaReef, you get their own personalized URL to your unique profile,  called a &quot;Pavilion&quot;. On your pavilion, your company can post links to  media, pictures, and stay connected to their customers through competitions and  Stream updates.</p></div>
